      chat surface intent routing — qualifies for FULL per task-execute Step 0.5).
      Output the mandatory RIGOR LEVEL declaration block.
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Read `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` and confirm task 019 status is 🔲, parallel-safe
      = ✅, wave P2-G5. Read `current-task.md` to confirm no conflicting task is
