      mocked `chatSession` + `documentId` inputs; (c) back-compat — wizard
      consumer outside ConversationPane is unaffected (regression guard).
      Test files live under
      `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/SlashCommandMenu/__tests__/`
      and `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/conversation/__tests__/`
      following existing test patterns.
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Spaarke Dev Smoke Test (Tri-Mode End-to-End)">
      Deploy the SpaarkeAi shell to Spaarke Dev (via `code-page-deploy` if a
      solution rebuild is needed, or rely on local dev server if the deployment
      surface allows). Manually exercise all three branches:
