        (c) Without uploaded files, without active document → invoke
            `/summarize` → confirm the "Upload the file(s) you'd like me to
            summarize" interjection appears in the chat thread; no playbook
            invocation; no error.
      Capture screenshots / DevTools network capture in task notes.
    </step>
    <step order="9" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
      Walk through every &lt;acceptance-criterion&gt; below and confirm each is
      testable + passing. Record evidence per criterion in task notes.
      Confirm publish-size delta = 0 MB (frontend-only; no BFF changed).
    </step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `code-review` skill against the modified files
      (`slashCommandMenu.types.ts` + `ConversationPane.tsx` + new test files).
